name: 3D SuperBike Traffic Rush Racing - High Speed Highway Rider: FREE GAME
name_original: 3D SuperBike Traffic Rush Racing - High Speed Highway Rider: FREE GAME
description:
Hop on your Superbike and rev your engines. It's time for the craziest traffic racing you've ever seen. Blast through traffic, firing nitro boosts grabbing powerups and collecting coins. Upgrade to a faster ride and go farther. Race through several different environments for a new experience. It's free so download it today!

Features
• 5 Different Motorcycles to choose from
• Awesome 3D graphics
• Nitro Boost, coin magnets and other powerups
• Several different environments to drive through
• Boost to pop wheelies
